{
  "stem": "6736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Somebody told me about it-- but they say they cannot find the Pole.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "That he run away-- when I was in Cracow after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they killed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "In 1942, when I came to Plaszow, it was, as I said before, Miller.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "From Plaszow, we would go every week to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I see my uncle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I go to have a bed, and had some food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I will take some stuff with me so I would have it for the week in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Until Amon Goeth came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Amon Goeth came to Plaszow either the very end of '42 or beginning of '43.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "The first thing he did Friday morning when he came in, he assembled us on the appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He killed the chief of the Jewish police and his assistant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was the chief of the police, and Goldberg was his assistant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And that time a Jewish policeman, Chelowicz, who became commander of the camp, I knew him, he lived on [NON-ENGLISH] 6.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we would go to the Vistula.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And he would always send me to the store to buy him a couple cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And he would always tell me, if you gonna hold it strong, and you gonna break the cigarettes, I break your neck.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was watching, and he was saying, [NON-ENGLISH]. .",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means Mother Maria.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's going to kill all of them people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went in from the appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I opened up a window.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I told him run away to the window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was working in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In [NON-ENGLISH], there were every day shooting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Amon Goeth, when his maid, a Jewish maid, put down the food for him, he wouldn't eat a lunch or breakfast or dinner if you didn't see Jewish blood.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
